{"tid":1623150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"South Park 最新一集《Band in China》被禁討論 S23E02成敏感詞","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:30:02.000Z","uid":56533,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"11af068574881d89418d37f47afc07a3d5534d91","tid":1623150,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:38:39.000Z","msg":"港稱《衰仔樂園 》的美國卡通《South Park》，一向以抵死爛口見稱，最新一集《Band in China》講述主角一班人組成的金屬樂隊要到「China」發展，卻遭到政府監控創作及強行改造成男團，這一集仲有小熊維尼出現在監獄之中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3365025/org/07d2bd334818d19322380b3c37406f4e.png/KkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3365025%2Forg%2F07d2bd334818d19322380b3c37406f4e.png%2FKkYPE_lY1IeR9eiQZeoM2Gv0SBb29GRt5d3YR-Xd2Ec&h=e7834e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSouth Park 今集《Band in China》主要分為兩條故事線，在美國種植大麻的 Randy  (港譯：子祥 ，因他樣子像林子祥！) 想到「China」擴展市場，當然他一落機就遭到拘捕，然後他被送往勞改營，在營中他遇到因「樣貌」而被監禁的小熊維尼及豬仔，之後他亦遇上希望到「China」做生意，而極度「愛國」的米老鼠，Randy 從中學懂了做生意之道。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Stan 與一眾主角成立了一隊死亡金屬樂隊，有經理人帶他們衝出 South Park，往「China」發展，但因為歌詞及風格問題，樂隊的創作一直「被指導」，Stan 在壓迫之下有了新想法打入「China」市場。樂隊成員改變風格成為「Finger Band」，即是一些老套，兼會在唱歌時用手指，指來指去的男團。Stan 最後醒覺不能因賺錢，而出賣靈魂，成為護旗男團。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3365035/org/4fdf7b0ae332a1013e6ed1e927744555.png/p7pdKa57sc4xMGddUt-EmjqrUXHkcsC5cJisc3CYrHM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3365035%2Forg%2F4fdf7b0ae332a1013e6ed1e927744555.png%2Fp7pdKa57sc4xMGddUt-EmjqrUXHkcsC5cJisc3CYrHM&h=4fb6550c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3365034/org/c18a80ba02caa584450792c958c47977.png/W2ItYUpXGHtmp9h51z0Q3p2R5jbzOd4WcWdFSnFnRUo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3365034%2Forg%2Fc18a80ba02caa584450792c958c47977.png%2FW2ItYUpXGHtmp9h51z0Q3p2R5jbzOd4WcWdFSnFnRUo&h=d4be6f26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在視頻網站 bilibili，之前會有網民非法上載 South Park (南方公園) 以往的集數，在《Band in China》推出後，網站積極進行「反侵權」行動，所有相關 South Park 的視頻一概移除，但在百度貼吧，還可以見到「南方公園吧」，卻完全沒有關於新一集的討論，真正做到「Ban in China」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3365039/org/71eadcc4cad6e0d6b720a810b7fbe4f2.png/7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3365039%2Forg%2F71eadcc4cad6e0d6b720a810b7fbe4f2.png%2F7YX2dDb94iqVSMbsZdv7XNHu5Ze2laVZzGUNPcxlDT0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=098605ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyBUyn46b1c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQyBUyn46b1c&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=8fab9084\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyBUyn46b1c</a>"},{"pid":"7f49af692b0d7a149d551cabb425d0ea64cc8359","tid":1623150,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:39:08.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3303f79e6f23253877439070eebc8de4f1caaacb","tid":1623150,"uid":4290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:49:04.000Z","msg":"lol"},{"pid":"1f59ac3bc2daa15d86c10d320f26fb77a6536491","tid":1623150,"uid":38049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:58:36.000Z","msg":"中國人辛勞工作，放工之後畀政府虐打，所以要享受美國優質大麻舒緩吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0083bfb140bb4466aa9f33ab54899ad0d5f04c01","tid":1623150,"uid":180931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:53:51.000Z","msg":"一直最愛就係south park"},{"pid":"56659dfd10a0291a9988c95cbb7c234f69ee1a76","tid":1623150,"uid":103976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T16:58:25.000Z","msg":"呢集係神作之中嘅神作<br />\n屌柒埋班放棄美國價值觀嘅豬hi"},{"pid":"c3061ebdf753a6147136f41b5d55c1f8d6198521","tid":1623150,"uid":87360,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"連標題都食埋字:<br />\n&quot;band&quot; 諧音 &quot;banned&quot;"},{"pid":"21c2dd115a6bf30e471fa64f43e4977385ceb959","tid":1623150,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:02:12.000Z","msg":"剛剛睇完，推爆佢"},{"pid":"49fea5575adf375b7f86806260cb5f425f5ba31e","tid":1623150,"uid":212796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"Finger bang 呀"},{"pid":"a364f96369b64445ae049e40d8285ee9cd67248d","tid":1623150,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">既然尋日咁回應,唔知&quot;Shots!!!&quot;呢集會係點</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_South_Park_episodes#Season_23_(2019)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_South_Park_episodes%23Season_23_%282019%29&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=efe04970\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_South_Park_episodes#Season_23_(2019)</a>"}]}